snippet.title: New York Comic Con
snippet.description:
NYCC is the largest pop culture convention on the East Coast and the only one that takes place in the comic book, publishing, media, and licensing capital of the world - Gotham City. 

Our show floor plays host to the latest in comics, graphic novels, anime, manga, video games, toys, movies, and television, our panels give fans a chance to interact with their favorite creators, and our screening rooms feature premieres of films and TV shows months before they hit either big or small screens!

Our YouTube channel also hosts video content from other shows from ReedPop - the world's leading provider of Pop Culture events - as well as brand new digital content from the Metaverse!

Get your pop culture fix and all the latest NYCC news on https://www.findthemetaverse.com/
